Description: U-Boot and source-built OpenSBI FIP for Milk-V Duo 256M
 Builds U-Boot for the Milk-V Duo 256M from upstream U-Boot sources,
 builds OpenSBI from source, embeds an upstream-kernel-based board DTB,
 sets the default U-Boot environment for distroboot DT selection, and packages
 the resulting firmware artifacts as a Debian package.
